Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.50,0:02:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你呼唤我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:03:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.60,0:03:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将这红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.90,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.90,0:03:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.40,0:03:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又看见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过有张海报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.30,0:04:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马戏团的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马戏团的海报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.00,0:04:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}流浪艺人之夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}蓝字：欢乐马戏团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.80,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人愉快的欢乐马戏团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空中踩钢锁 驯兽表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.10,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年我们又来了 欢乐马戏团 一年一度的欢乐马戏哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的是马戏团呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西居然还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧小姐 进来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么让他发现的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.80,0:05:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 是谁登录了地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想进行采访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 说实话很吃惊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到还能看见这样的马戏团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺怀念的啊怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么您是特意从东京来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.20,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然在网上看见 很感兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 你这种人早点去死好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.00,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用理他们的 每天晚上都这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.50,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像那对夫妻的仪式一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是情人的登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过去年之前一直是那个家伙扮演的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是世界第一的飞刀手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不要冲着我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到那边去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.70,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 在这种地方做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在等爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来采访的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么要来这种马戏团采访呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.80,0:08:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.90,0:08:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨你会什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不是马戏团的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然有些本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看 让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从插剑的箱子里脱身的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能稍微见一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些话想问她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.70,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的 只是觉得她演技真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可是团长的宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你特意从东京跑来的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.30,0:09:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 听说是来采访的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是有怪人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然采访这种蹩脚马戏团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本上听名字就够白痴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么欢乐马戏团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是这么觉得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到这边来 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我 目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.20,0:10:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 我不碰你 你赶快走开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.30,0:10:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱好不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.20,0:10:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要再想报仇什么的蠢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你登录了地狱通信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕吧 不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你带到他触手不及的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你跟我走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放开我 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 别出那么大声 我是来帮你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可为难我了 兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了只说话的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.90,0:11:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骨女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿目 快放我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不是那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为肯定没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之先吃饭吧 回头再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又在演出中出错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.40,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是有谁在我鞋跟上动了手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 振作点 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩正在挨打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 救救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.30,0:13:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她满身伤痕 一直在挨打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是身上哪有伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.90,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双胞胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是箱子脱身的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨团长的 是另一个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里看到那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像牢房一样的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.80,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}找不到家的小云雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.10,0:15:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an9}在无垠田野上的麦穗间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}虽啼叫呼唤母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.30,0:15:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an9}却只闻风中麦穗喃喃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.10,0:15:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是 已经解开了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,详细情况之后再解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧逃离这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会被送往地狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 赶快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么 放开我 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}找不到家的迷途小云雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fn华文细黑\an7}おうち忘れたまよいごの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.10,0:16:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}如今孤独地躲在麦田里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.10,0:16:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fn华文细黑\an7}ひばりはひとり麦の中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真努力啊 佩服佩服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是奖励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.60,0:17:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}山中狐狸虽不啼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.60,0:17:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fn华文细黑\an7}お山の狐は　なかぬけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.20,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}凄凉寂寞明月光 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.20,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fn华文细黑\an7}暮れてさみしい　月あかり
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.90,0:18:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出去 尽说些莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.90,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.00,0:18:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.40,0:18:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱马戏团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明星终于要出场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很期待哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 快骑上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骑这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点就要被那些手抓住了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我怎么可能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连这点事都做不到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.10,0:19:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.50,0:20:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能坚持多久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那便向姐姐谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜 知道那孩子因为你受了多少苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.20,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己得宠就陷害姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真肮脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向姐姐谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙我总是不能出头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一个人登上舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.70,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要一个人就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个人就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她这么说 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.90,0:21:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.30,0:21:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.70,0:21:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.30,0:21:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下 我叫你停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.00,0:21:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.60,0:22:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快停下 不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要离开了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.10,0:22:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿目呢 谁看见阿目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.10,0:22:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,团长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.50,0:22:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 很合适呢 由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.80,0:22:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是绝配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.60,0:22:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.00,0:22:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.30,0:23:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
