Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.70,0:24:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.50,0:24:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是这样说的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.50,0:24:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是被浓雾笼罩的静养院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.30,0:24:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.10,0:24:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.00,0:24:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去 不会让你将人流放到地狱去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.60,0:24:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 不可以去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.70,0:24:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一 听到八音盒的声音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.50,0:25:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&\an7}下集
